                    <span>That's what I was thinking as I watched this movie.  Sure, the music is corny, but the footage is fantastic!  It had me itching to get my bikes out of the garage.  The movie awakens that urge to compete!  A really superb film-if you love motorcycles, then you'll love this!  (Just don't watch it when you can't ride, I did and had spring fever big time from it!)</span>
                  
              
